      "role": "User",
      "timestamp": "07:25",
      "timestampManuallyEdited": false
    },
    {
      "content": "岁月蹉跎，人已将老之类的",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "User",
      "timestamp": "07:25",
      "timestampManuallyEdited": false
    },
    {
      "content": "你不觉得奇怪吗？你今年才多大啊",
