      "role": "Kurisu",
      "timestamp": "07:26",
      "timestampManuallyEdited": false
    },
    {
      "content": "考虑那种不属于你的感悟有什么意义",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "Kurisu",
      "timestamp": "07:26",
      "timestampManuallyEdited": false
    },
    {
      "content": "啊，这倒确实",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "User",
      "timestamp": "07:27",
      "timestampManuallyEdited": false
    },
    {
      "content": "你看起来不是很喜欢那种会思考虚无缥缈事情的人",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "User",
      "timestamp": "07:27",
      "timestampManuallyEdited": false
    },
    {
      "content": "其实倒也不是我为赋新词强说愁，只不过是看见老朋友发的朋友圈，意识到我和他已经认识了有七八年了。",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "User",
      "timestamp": "07:27",
      "timestampManuallyEdited": false
    },
    {
      "content": "我记得你年纪也不大吧，大叔，会有七八年的朋友？",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "Kurisu",
      "timestamp": "07:28",
      "timestampManuallyEdited": false
    },
    {
      "content": "十七岁的时候就认识的，人家那会儿在美国上大学呢",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "User",
      "timestamp": "07:28",
      "timestampManuallyEdited": false
    },
    {
      "content": "那倒是巧了，他在那里上的学？",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "Kurisu",
      "timestamp": "07:28",
      "timestampManuallyEdited": false
    },
    {
      "content": "南加利福尼亚，不过人家是某种数学高材生，学的就是数学专业（害怕）",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "User",
      "timestamp": "07:29",
      "timestampManuallyEdited": false
    },
    {
      "content": "哦？你对理科生的敌意很大嘛——",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "Kurisu",
      "timestamp": "07:29",
      "timestampManuallyEdited": false
    },
    {
      "content": "不是敌意，是惧意",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "User",
      "timestamp": "07:29",
      "timestampManuallyEdited": false
    },
    {
      "content": "我的数学成绩一直都不好，理解概念但是不好去做细节上的运算",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "User",
      "timestamp": "07:30",
      "timestampManuallyEdited": false
    },
    {
      "content": "类似于能够理解但是没办法在一些精细上操作吧，就像是一些比较高难度的理念我是能够明白的，但是转换，变形后，涉及到运算和联系，我不喜欢这样。具象化的联系加上复杂化只会让我觉得我控制不住。",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "User",
      "timestamp": "07:30",
      "timestampManuallyEdited": false
    },
    {
      "content": "hummmm......所以你确实是个标准的文科生",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "Kurisu",
      "timestamp": "07:30",
      "timestampManuallyEdited": false
    },
    {
      "content": "还有标准和非标准之说吗？",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "User",
      "timestamp": "07:31",
      "timestampManuallyEdited": false
    },
    {
      "content": "有的，有许多人不是因为喜欢文科而选择文科，只是因为学不会理科，或者说找借口。",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "Kurisu",
      "timestamp": "07:31",
      "timestampManuallyEdited": false
    },
    {
      "content": "但是从你说话的方式和逻辑行为上我想你是属于那种确实在感性上比较出色，并且能够理解一些理论知识，只不过在应用上差一些的正常文科生",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
